{"id":389886,"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/21/56/215628.jpg","floor":"#1","group":"番組WIKI計画","groupHref":"/group/wiki","groupThumb":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/icon/m/000/00/01/128.jpg","message":"看了一下<a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/637114346\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener noreferrer\" class=\"l\">这篇文章</a>的内容，发现issue是一个连载相关期刊的概念。但issue中似乎只会有单个漫画系列的内容，类似于单行本性质，与一般印象中jump的那种一期内有很多漫画系列的刊物不同。不过issue好像也是印刷完一遍即止，与后者类似。<br><br>那么假如说要建立一个美漫系列，比如以这个作品的<a href=\"https://www.goodreads.com/series/355744-doctor-who-the-thirteenth-doctor-single-issues\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener noreferrer\" class=\"l\">issue</a>和<a href=\"https://www.goodreads.com/series/246180-doctor-who-the-thirteenth-doctor-titan-comics\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener noreferrer\" class=\"l\">volume</a>，那么该系列的单行本是该按照issue来修，将issue视为最初的单行本，而volume作为总集的不同版本；还是该直接按照volume来修，忽视issue？","time":"2023-11-15 23:28","title":"美漫系列书籍是以issue作为单行本还是以volume作为单行本？","userId":"a446344243","userName":"pencil","userSign":"(good)"}